## Overview

Refactor Jekyll site from monolithic style architecture to modular, maintainable design system. **Parallel-optimized execution**: Phases 1-3 run concurrently; Phase 4 integrates; Phases 5-6 run sequentially.

### Dependency Graph

```mermaid
graph TD
    P1[Phase 01: CSS Variables] --> P2[Phase 02: CSS Components]
    P2 --> P4[Phase 04: Layout Refactor]
    P3[Phase 03: JS Modules] --> P4
    P4 --> P5[Phase 05: Accessibility]
    P4 --> P6[Phase 06: Performance]

    style P1 fill:#e3f2fd
    style P2 fill:#fff3e0
    style P3 fill:#e3f2fd
