### Parallelization Strategy

| Wave | Phases | Description |
|------|--------|-------------|
| **Wave 1** (Parallel) | 01, 02, 03 | Independent foundation work |
| **Wave 2** (Sequential) | 04 | Integration point - depends on 01-03 |
| **Wave 3** (Sequential) | 05, 06 | Quality & optimization gates |

